      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, presented in absolute mint, showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster and mirror-like finish with no chips or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smells like new, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear. Every component functions perfectly, reflecting the meticulous care and climate-controlled storage this car has received throughout its life.",
