    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior has minor cosmetic blemishes, such as small scratches and stone chips. The interior is well-maintained with only light signs of use. All mechanical systems are functioning correctly, and the car has been regularly serviced.",
