    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular driving, while the interior shows light wear but no tears or major stains. Mechanically, it runs very well, with all major systems functioning as they should and a consistent service history. Buyers can expect a dependable daily driver that has been cared for, though it is not in showroom condition.",
